
---

## File: `.gitignore`

Paste this:

```gitignore
# Build output
bin/
obj/
out/
publish/

# User-specific files
*.user
*.suo
*.rsuser
.vs/
.vscode/*.user

# Rider
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Environment / secrets
.env
.env.*
*.secrets.json
appsettings.Development.local.json

# Test results
TestResults/
coverage/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

# NuGet
*.nupkg
packages/
.nuget/

# Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

# SQLite local databases
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal